text: hey all - quick note on the retrospective and the feedback form. your feedback is very important. i want to give you some time to complete the form thoughtfully, so i’m moving our retrospective to friday.
let me know if you have any questions!

<@U04JZANJF> I have a question: I haven’t done one of these feedback forms yet; how are they used? Are they reviewed by you and/or someone else before the meeting, do we each discuss our own at the meeting, or something else?

Good question! They’re reviewed by me before the meeting. I’ll compile thoughts that seem to appear across feedback for us to discuss as a group and then open the floor to discuss anything that was important to them that might not have made it into the general group discussion.
